headline: 3 High-Yielding Dividend Stocks You Can Buy for Less Than $100
summary: Want some modestly priced stocks that also pay high dividends?  It can be challenging finding a quality stock that fits that criteria, but there are three that can be excellent options worth considering today: Realty Income (NYSE: O), AT&T (NYSE: T), and Toronto-Dominion Bank (NYSE: TD).
